    <releaseNotes>
    - New: Edit metadata dialog: Add the ability to trim covers manually, if automatic trimming is not satisfactory.
    - New: You can now show any metadata field below the covers in the cover grid view, not just title. To change the displayed field go to Preferences -- Look and Feel -- Cover Grid.
	- New: Allow searching for plugins by name in the install new plugins dialog
	- New: Kobo driver: Allow sending kepubs to older kobo devices as well, also add support for firmware 3.1
	- New: Allow viewer plugins to customize the viewer's user interface
	- Fixed: Table of Contents Editor: Handle generating ToC from headings if the first heading level in the document is not h1 or the document skips some intermediate heading levels
	- Fixed: Update the metadata download and Get Books plugins for ozon.ru
	- Fixed: Fix sending by email not working on computers with non-ascii hostnames.
	- Fixed: Wireless driver: Fix launching programs from within calibre causing the wireless driver port to remain in use even after calibre is shutdown.
    - Improved News Source: Kommersant
	- Improved News Source: Pocket
	- Improved News Source: Heraldo de Aragon
	- Improved News Source: National Geographic Magazine
	- Improved News Source: Los Angeles Times
	- Improved News Source: Boerse Online
	- Improved News Source: Reuters
    </releaseNotes>
  </metadata>
</package>
